{"tid":1952611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★遭逢乾旱 泰國出口米價飆至6年半最貴","createTime":"2020-03-31T16:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T01:04:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"34b4ac8b8a9c103dc7d8fe2d1148f6cf327f06ef","tid":1952611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，由於泰國、越南今年遭逢乾旱，中國又在湄公河上游建水壩，越南快速都市化，以及疫情造成恐慌性搶購等影響，泰國出口的米價達每公噸550美元(約4,290港元)，為2013年8月以來新高；泰國為世界第2大稻米出口國，佔全球稻米出口比重達23%。<br />\n<br />\n由於泰國及越南稻米出口減少，美國農業部在2月時，下調全球稻米貿易總量70萬噸，至4,530萬噸；而2018年時，泰國出口了1,110萬噸稻米，但當地貿易商估計，今年泰國可能只能出口750萬噸稻米。<br />\n<br />\n泰國從去年8月雨季開始即逢乾旱問題，降雨量較往年低了30%，泰國匯商銀行預計，如果乾旱時間持續到6月，今年2至7月的稻米收成可能只有往年一半。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200331/bkn-20200331232805576-0331_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200331%2Fbkn-20200331232805576-0331_00842_001.html&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=b7a9df23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200331/bkn-20200331232805576-0331_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ce9b5235650b6ef793b46d68bd4fff9b499224c5","tid":1952611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229a39cf5fffca2ba7319b77d6efb6366a99ed3d","tid":1952611,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img3.secretchina.com/pic/2020